{"tid":453663,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"人在花蓮，好悶，你問我盡答","createTime":"2017-10-31T11:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T08:20:24.000Z","uid":2206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"743109a901c07b0bdec3fc718510747b3181784c","tid":453663,"uid":2206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:31:07.000Z","msg":"個夜市一陣就行完，好悶，有冇咩活動推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3bc3143dab2937ec8870bbc8c7947bcacd770c","tid":453663,"uid":14557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"無 8月去過真係好悶 不過個時好曬邊到都唔想去"},{"pid":"7c92b9c04ca4cd9e5dadc9f7513d53fff7ea7100","tid":453663,"uid":74122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:35:39.000Z","msg":"去左咩夜市？12月去花蓮兩日一夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531da966c3003cd5925ea97753e8b2ad9cadaccf","tid":453663,"uid":49754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:39:56.000Z","msg":"個夜市好19"},{"pid":"0803241dfd7b79acb7b97621aa4dc499792783a9","tid":453663,"uid":2206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去左咩夜市？12月去花蓮兩日一夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似得一個東大門夜市 入邊有4條街 都係食下嘢 玩下攤位同聽人唱下歌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538c9cb7a121fc3b91c387b41a5fe7bc0920d845","tid":453663,"uid":2206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個夜市好19</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但真係冇咩夜生活 去左一晚之後啲夜晚都唔知點過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba5917916404de85a0a61b6d5fd9be053035427","tid":453663,"uid":2206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無 8月去過真係好悶 不過個時好曬邊到都唔想去</blockquote><br />\n啲人仲話好好住 都唔知邊忽好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f372e2ae6ed56d7bd56fa7dd5f13ead7af7cc8a2","tid":453663,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:13:21.000Z","msg":"鄉下地方夜晚係無咩做架喇<br />\n花蓮市區有戲睇, 有K唱, 算係咁啦"},{"pid":"e912a292db29145cc639fa1a9338754e9db5c00a","tid":453663,"uid":2206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄉下地方夜晚係無咩做架喇<br />\n花蓮市區有戲睇, 有K唱, 算係咁啦</blockquote><br />\n係咪車站個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日去睇下先"},{"pid":"974c83b4f2e6d59722caeba5562865c36c9916b6","tid":453663,"uid":54812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"幾鐘意花蓮啲慢生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚唔好行夜市 去行大街 <br />\n有啲鋪頭又抵又好食<br />\n食過個刈包40台幣好食到不得了<br />\n仲有間食芋圓又係40又大碗又好食"},{"pid":"f727d01e5e494988b828c23df81928be57bb6732","tid":453663,"uid":33727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鄉下地方夜晚係無咩做架喇<br />\n花蓮市區有戲睇, 有K唱, 算係咁啦</blockquote><br />\n係咪車站個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日去睇下先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.showtimes.com.tw/corporations/3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.showtimes.com.tw%2Fcorporations%2F3&d=NmQg4hzuelNsIzkRmOffeBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=dd89d91c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.showtimes.com.tw/corporations/3</a><br />\n花蓮秀泰影城"},{"pid":"fb18bafcee476d70d2c3b40fd4e7a305e287e37f","tid":453663,"uid":123696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個夜市一陣就行完，好悶，有冇咩活動推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜市打鼓個女仔好似唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時間去埋台北囉<br />\n4個鐘車就到<br />\n<br />\n花蓮慢慢行都幾舒服<br />\n算多嘢食"},{"pid":"40c7ec55a35208fccced8f658748570e8bc5ae34","tid":453663,"uid":63328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:35:18.000Z","msg":"如果你會去瑞穗浸溫泉，哩間牛奶鍋好食<br />\n<br />\n綠精靈<br />\nNo. 52, Chenggong North Road, Ruisui Township, Hualien County, Taiwan 978<br />\n+886 3 887 6306<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/LMoRBgm3Bcm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FLMoRBgm3Bcm&d=NmQg4hzuelNsIzkRmOffeBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e557055d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/LMoRBgm3Bcm</a>"},{"pid":"6f7b5bbcd78174302bd1945c25033564cd8f9c9c","tid":453663,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"夜晚行去海邊幾好 feel<br />\n一個人去既會悶小小<br />\n去埋文創啦"},{"pid":"5514f9212b67f56efd85a37073104eb6cac110a6","tid":453663,"uid":2206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:07:42.000Z","msg":"Thanks bro<br />\n<br />\n有冇人玩過飛行傘同溯溪？好玩？"},{"pid":"9f000cfea9095cf85d0da02989adea35d063d3e3","tid":453663,"uid":2206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1380d0207fb5b7f1272efaaf3f9a80a1f341f4f","tid":453663,"uid":82224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:24:48.000Z","msg":"花蓮雞都無得叫，鄉下地方😂"},{"pid":"a45b473a87f3fee0fed13ebb1c04352f91f611b8","tid":453663,"uid":82887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"諗緊去多次台北定去花蓮好<br />\n未去過花蓮，都幾想去睇下風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ae0fed2e37733353458c9106d34e99c2e360b0","tid":453663,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"有無john 啲當地一日團 ? 咩太魯閣、七星潭嗰啲"},{"pid":"561d7bb6dc7a372267e2896036a35d9d51e33096","tid":453663,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite